RawQuestion: what age did william penn get married?
ProcessedQuestion: what age did william penn get married

Parses.Sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.083qr)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.083qr ns:people.person.spouse_s ?y .
?y ns:people.marriage.from ?x .
?y ns:people.marriage.type_of_union ns:m.04ztj .
}

RawQuestion: what is the name of the book hitler wrote in jail?
ProcessedQuestion: what is the name of the book hitler wrote in jail

Parses.Sparql:
#MANUAL SPARQL
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT  ?x
WHERE {
  ns:m.07_m9_ ns:book.book_subject.works ?x .
  ?x ns:book.written_work.date_written ?d .

  ns:m.07_m9_ ns:base.prison.prisoner.imprisoned ?y .
  ?y          ns:base.prison.imprisonment.from ?from ;
              ns:base.prison.imprisonment.to ?to .
  FILTER (xsd:dateTime(?d) - xsd:dateTime(?from) >= 0)
  FILTER (xsd:dateTime(?to) - xsd:dateTime(?d) >= 0)
}
